        "founder_content": {
          "type": "content",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "The Jolene Team",
            "content": "<p>It started with frustration. We were tired of bitter cold brew and oat milk lattes that tasted like flavored water. Every morning felt like a compromise between ethics and taste.</p><p>So we spent months perfecting a 12-hour slow brewing process that extracts maximum flavor without the acidity. We partnered with Fair Trade certified farms and sourced the creamiest oat milk we could find. After countless taste tests, Jolene Coffee was born.</p><p>Today, we're building a community of coffee lovers who refuse to settle. Every bottle represents our commitment to bold flavor, ethical sourcing, and moments that matter.</p>",
            "button_label": "",
            "url": "",
            "show_image_as_background": false,
            "enable_autoplay": true,
            "enable_mute_toggle": true,
